title: Lick Library -  Play - Easy Acoustic Rock - Volume 1 - DVD (2004
description:
Suitable for beginners up to the intermediate guitarist, Jamie Humphries teaches the nuts and bolts of eight classic acoustic rock songs. View Humphries' guitar playing up close and get your fingers around the chops and skills that make these tunes so great.

 Includes these songs:

 Babylon [Gray, David]
 High And Dry [Radiohead]
 Karma Police [Radiohead]
 Losing My Religion [REM]
 One [U2]
 Sing [Travis]
 Wild Wood [Weller, Paul]
 Yellow [Coldplay]
